metadata.name: Hustleverse Passport NFT 2022 - 2023
metadata.description:
This token grants access to the Hustleverse Passport NFT Discord community until September 2023.

Our community consists of builders and operators who want to learn about and transition their career from Web2 to Web3.

We do this by hosting virtual events with founders, thought leaders, and speakers to teach you about Web3 tools and what Web3 employers are looking for.

We hope you enjoy your time with us in the Hustleverse.

Note: This pass will expire on September 30, 2023.
